gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Lib

Class Flow

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Lib.BitMaskBase
      • gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Lib.Flow

  • public class Flow
extends BitMaskBase
    This class provides methods of combining Lvg output records by specifying different rules. It is utilized under Lvg Output filter options.

    History:

    • SCR-11, chlu, 06-04-12, Fixed compile error due to JDK upgrade
    Version:
    V-2013
    Author:
    NLM NLS Development Team
